                                    <pre><code># dpkg-reconfigure openssh-server</code></pre>
                                    <h2>Step 4: Auto Login with SSH enabled</h2>
                                    <p>This is no required but if you want to be able to remote access your Raspberry Pi via ssh you can perform these steps below.</p>
                                    <p><a href="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_04_01_04.Still005.jpg"><img data-attachment-id="1448" data-permalink="https://www.novaspirit.com/2018/04/24/kali-linux-raspberry-pi-3b-monitor-mode/sequence-01-00_04_01_04-still005/" data-orig-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_04_01_04.Still005.jpg" data-orig-size="1920,1080" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Sequence 01.00_04_01_04.Still005" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_04_01_04.Still005-300x169.jpg" data-large-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_04_01_04.Still005-1024x576.jpg" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-1448" src="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_04_01_04.Still005-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_04_01_04.Still005-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_04_01_04.Still005-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_04_01_04.Still005-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_04_01_04.Still005-1080x608.jpg 1080w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_04_01_04.Still005-600x338.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></p>
                                    <p>these following command well removed the old settings for ssh in the boot up process and setup ssh to boot on runtime level 3, 4, and 5.</p>
                                    <p><code># update-rc.d -f ssh remove<br />
                                            #&nbsp;update-rc.d&nbsp;-f&nbsp;ssh&nbsp;defaults<br />
                                            #&nbsp;service&nbsp;ssh&nbsp;restart<br />
                                            #&nbsp;update-rc.d&nbsp;-f&nbsp;ssh&nbsp;enable&nbsp;3&nbsp;4</code>&nbsp;5</p>
                                    <p>and now we need to enable auto login to kali which is required for ssh to start. This step will require your Rpi to reboot.</p>
                                    <p><a href="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_05_01_09.Still007.jpg"><img data-attachment-id="1450" data-permalink="https://www.novaspirit.com/2018/04/24/kali-linux-raspberry-pi-3b-monitor-mode/sequence-01-00_05_01_09-still007/" data-orig-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_05_01_09.Still007.jpg" data-orig-size="1920,1080" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Sequence 01.00_05_01_09.Still007" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_05_01_09.Still007-300x169.jpg" data-large-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_05_01_09.Still007-1024x576.jpg" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-1450" src="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_05_01_09.Still007-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_05_01_09.Still007-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_05_01_09.Still007-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_05_01_09.Still007-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_05_01_09.Still007-1080x608.jpg 1080w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_05_01_09.Still007-600x338.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></p>
                                    <pre><code># /usr/local/src/re4son-kernel_4.9.60-20180404/re4son-pi-tft-setup -a root</code></pre>
                                    <h2>Step 5: Enabling Monitoring mode</h2>
                                    <p>Now for the fun!! this image has nexmon patch enabled which allows for the onboard wifi controller to use monitor mode, a mode usually required if you want to use airmon-ng tools</p>
                                    <p>This command below will add a monitor mode interface</p>
                                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                    <p><a href="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_06_32_15.Still008.jpg"><img data-attachment-id="1451" data-permalink="https://www.novaspirit.com/2018/04/24/kali-linux-raspberry-pi-3b-monitor-mode/sequence-01-00_06_32_15-still008/" data-orig-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_06_32_15.Still008.jpg" data-orig-size="1920,1080" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Sequence 01.00_06_32_15.Still008" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_06_32_15.Still008-300x169.jpg" data-large-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_06_32_15.Still008-1024x576.jpg" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-1451" src="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_06_32_15.Still008-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_06_32_15.Still008-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_06_32_15.Still008-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_06_32_15.Still008-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_06_32_15.Still008-1080x608.jpg 1080w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Sequence-01.00_06_32_15.Still008-600x338.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></p>
                                    <pre><code># iw phy phy0 interface add mon0 type monitor</code></pre>
                                    <p>and to enable the monitor mode type</p>
                                    <p><a href="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ifconfig.jpg"><img data-attachment-id="1454" data-permalink="https://www.novaspirit.com/2018/04/24/kali-linux-raspberry-pi-3b-monitor-mode/ifconfig/" data-orig-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ifconfig.jpg" data-orig-size="1399,116" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="ifconfig" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ifconfig-300x25.jpg" data-large-file="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ifconfig-1024x85.jpg" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-1454" src="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ifconfig-1024x85.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="85" srcset="https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ifconfig-1024x85.jpg 1024w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ifconfig-300x25.jpg 300w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ifconfig-768x64.jpg 768w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ifconfig-1080x90.jpg 1080w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ifconfig-600x50.jpg 600w, https://www.novaspirit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/ifconfig.jpg 1399w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></p>
                                    <pre><code># ifconfig mon0 up</code></pre>
